Diamond Platnumz' record label WCB has signed its second female artiste. Her social media name is Zuchu. Zuchu comes from a musical family as she is the daughter of revered Taarab crooner Khadija Kopa. â€œWe introduce to you the new queen of Bongo Flava,'' Diamond wrote on Instagram. "She is a daughter of the queen who has a voice like a parrot. She has been groomed well and she is now ready. It is time for the world to enjoy her talent." Zuchu responded, "It's a huge honour to finally fulfil my dream. Na pia ni baraka na bahati kubwa sana to be signed under the Biggest Label In Africa WCB. "Thank you Diamond Platnumz and whole of WCB management for believing in my talent. Expect the absolute best."